  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Hell's most exclusive casino! where demons deal with the cards and the stakes are your very soul. With its stunning anime-inspired visuals, relaxing atmosphere, and addictive gameplay, Soultaker is the ultimate card game experience for gamers of all skill levels.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/d8e11fb2619d090cc19462a1eba360b7.poster.avif?t=1754923889\" width=754 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/d8e11fb2619d090cc19462a1eba360b7.webm?t=1754923889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/d8e11fb2619d090cc19462a1eba360b7.mp4?t=1754923889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play against the demon dealers in the underworld as you compete for cash and glory. Each dealer has their own unique style, so choose wisely to gain the upper hand. With customizable card art and table sets, you can create a gaming experience that's truly your own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/d48fc40a7e8c3bb47f70ed9c31939c88.poster.avif?t=1754923889\" width=754 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/d48fc40a7e8c3bb47f70ed9c31939c88.webm?t=1754923889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/d48fc40a7e8c3bb47f70ed9c31939c88.mp4?t=1754923889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>But beware - the road to victory is fraught with danger. Will you have the skills and luck to win your way out of Hell? Or will you be trapped forever, at the mercy of the devilish dealers? Play Soultaker and find out!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/9a8875ad7c38ee5afa488f33c68f7c96.poster.avif?t=1754923889\" width=754 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/9a8875ad7c38ee5afa488f33c68f7c96.webm?t=1754923889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212830/extras/9a8875ad7c38ee5afa488f33c68f7c96.mp4?t=1754923889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><i><br>Engaging card game with simple controls and addictive gameplay<br>Anime-inspired visuals and a relaxing atmosphere<br>Play against demon dealers with their own unique style and backstory<br>Customize your gaming experience with customizable card art, table sets<br>Earn cash and use it to buy outfits for the dealer and other customization options<br>Additional demon dealers representing other casino games </i></strong>",
